This is, surprisely, onPHP repository (or just checkout).
UTF8 is mandatory.

GIT: git://git.shadanakar.org/onPHP

	Access:
	
	git clone git://git.shadanakar.org/onPHP (read-only)
	git clone git+ssh://git@git.shadanakar.org/onPHP (read/write)
	
	Config:
	
	git config user.name "Your Name"
	git config user.email you@example.com

	git config color.diff auto
	git config color.status auto
	git config color.branch auto	

Web:

	http://onphp.org/
	http://onphp.ru/

Forum:

	http://onphp.org/forum
	http://onphp.ru/forum

